body:
This is the final set of GT for next pre-release:

Updated new conditions for Run2 MC DIGI-RECO campaign.
Added Egamma PF Cluster corrections in all scenarios (so removed the ESPrefer in RecoParticleFlow/PFClusterProducer/python/particleFlowClusterECAL_cfi.py);
Updated hadron PF calibrations for Run2 MC, and new IOV appended to the HLT and re-reco GT;
Removed unused records for old 3x3 APE in all the GT;
Removed unsupported SIM geometry scenarios;
Use the correct key for HI Run2 MC (as in #7704).

In addition - current fastim configs miss the run2 setup for digitizers in fastsim. This PR takes care of that (will be more robust once we get eras working)
